name: A & W Food Services of Canada Inc.
longDescription: A & W Food Services of Canada Inc. owns and operates quick-service restaurants. The Company develops and franchises restaurants that retails prepared foods, snacks, frozen cold brew, and drinks for on-premise consumption, as well as offers food service and restaurant management solutions.
